## Important Notes

- Follow the dependency structure defined in tasks.json when implementing features
- Use Task Master to track development progress
- Ensure comprehensive error handling for all Bluetooth operations
- Maintain cross-platform compatibility where possible, with Windows as primary target
- Keep performance impacts minimal, especially for system tray and background operations
- Follow Rust best practices for memory management and concurrency
- Apply consistent theming using the Catppuccin Mocha color scheme

